<section id="services" class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">What I Build</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Complex multi-tenant applications for teams that need things done right the first time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="card p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-6 text-blue-600">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.25 6a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h13.5a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v12a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H5.25a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V6Zm3.97.97a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0l2.25 2.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-2.25 2.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06-1.06l1.72-1.72-1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06Zm4.28 4.28a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h3a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5h-3Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Multi-Tenant SaaS Foundations</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Account and tenancy boundaries, role-based access, audit trails, and admin tooling.
          The infrastructure layer your product needs before you can ship features.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-green-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-6 text-green-600">
            <path d="M10.464 8.746c.227-.18.497-.311.786-.394v2.795a2.252 2.252 0 0 1-.786-.393c-.394-.313-.546-.681-.546-1.004 0-.323.152-.691.546-1.004ZM12.75 15.662v-2.824c.347.085.664.228.921.421.427.32.579.686.579.991 0 .305-.152.671-.579.991a2.534 2.534 0 0 1-.921.42Z" />
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2.25c-5.385 0-9.75 4.365-9.75 9.75s4.365 9.75 9.75 9.75 9.75-4.365 9.75-9.75S17.385 2.25 12 2.25ZM12.75 6a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v.816a3.836 3.836 0 0 0-1.72.756c-.712.566-1.112 1.35-1.112 2.178 0 .829.4 1.612 1.113 2.178.502.4 1.102.647 1.719.756v2.978a2.536 2.536 0 0 1-.921-.421l-.879-.66a.75.75 0 0 0-.9 1.2l.879.66c.533.4 1.169.645 1.821.75V18a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0v-.81a4.124 4.124 0 0 0 1.821-.749c.745-.559 1.179-1.344 1.179-2.191 0-.847-.434-1.632-1.179-2.191a4.122 4.122 0 0 0-1.821-.75V8.354c.29.082.559.213.786.393l.415.33a.75.75 0 0 0 .933-1.175l-.415-.33a3.836 3.836 0 0 0-1.719-.755V6Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Revenue + Onboarding Pipelines</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Billing systems, subscription or invoicing flows, usage metering, and
          KYC onboarding checklists. Get paid reliably and onboard users safely.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-6 text-purple-600">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.625 1.5c-1.036 0-1.875.84-1.875 1.875v17.25c0 1.035.84 1.875 1.875 1.875h12.75c1.035 0 1.875-.84 1.875-1.875V12.75A3.75 3.75 0 0 0 16.5 9h-1.875a1.875 1.875 0 0 1-1.875-1.875V5.25A3.75 3.75 0 0 0 9 1.5H5.625ZM7.5 15a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h7.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-7.5A.75.75 0 0 1 7.5 15Zm.75 2.25a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5H12a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5H8.25Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            <path d="M12.971 1.816A5.23 5.23 0 0 1 14.25 5.25v1.875c0 .207.168.375.375.375H16.5a5.23 5.23 0 0 1 3.434 1.279 9.768 9.768 0 0 0-6.963-6.963Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Workflow-Heavy Domain Apps</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Document generation, approval flows, bulk import/export, Excel integrations,
          and stakeholder notifications. The operational core of your business logic.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">If this sounds like your product, send a short note&mdash;I'll reply with next steps.</p>
      <%= link_to "Contact Heftydev", "#contact", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
